{"title":"EI-2024","guid":"","filepath":"/Users/criaah/Vault/📚 Resources/Mapas-Mentales/Entidades clínicas/General/EI-2024.smmx","root":{"id":"0","parent":"-1","text":"EI","guid":"X1mIkyXUvzKzkhQc6UGikw","children":[{"id":"1","parent":"0","text":"Endocarditis\\NInfecciosa (EI)","guid":"","children":[{"id":"2","parent":"1","text":"Definición: Infección del endocardio, afectando generalmente válvulas cardíacas.","guid":"4PhgnkuHHkz-zjDli0I81Q","children":[]},{"id":"3","parent":"1","text":"Etiología","guid":"N3ZMBr5DCIuqPQdPgezgww","children":[{"id":"4","parent":"3","text":"Bacteriemia: + frecuente → procedimientos dentales, cirugías,\\Ninfecciones primarias distantes, inyecciones no estériles.","guid":"kXG7v8cAmg61vRd7rexx3g","children":[]}]},{"id":"5","parent":"1","text":"Tipos:","guid":"3JLXWH0k9wLvkfWasPOycQ","children":[{"id":"6","parent":"5","text":"Aguda: ⬆ velocidad de desarrollo (horas o días) → Staphylococcus aureus\\N→ destrucción rápida del tejido endocárdico.","guid":"4zTHb2c73uW7fuv3Lm3b3Q","children":[]},{"id":"7","parent":"5","text":"Subaguda: Progresiva (semanas o meses) → Streptococcus viridans → afecta personas\\Ncon daño valvular previo, defectos cardíacos estructurales o prótesis valvulares.","guid":"HBS61ZOPBOVC3IHAkXFRWw","children":[]}]},{"id":"8","parent":"1","text":"Clínica","guid":"eEDuYqAxVm6bwiK1l5VwSQ","children":[{"id":"9","parent":"8","text":"Síntomas constitucionales: fatiga, fiebre/escalofríos, malestar general.","guid":"8Efd88pvn7IkuwfIdCS3hQ","children":[]},{"id":"10","parent":"8","text":"Cambios cardíacos: nuevo o modificado soplo cardíaco, signos de IC.","guid":"e-JzAnHWifUPnpcTkUgI7g","children":[]},{"id":"11","parent":"8","text":"Manifestaciones sistémicas: glomerulonefritis, ACV embólico séptico.","guid":"SGHNu7zs5Mzm0N9_y-ykUA","children":[]}]},{"id":"12","parent":"1","text":"Diagnóstico","guid":"Wrb1zGwcpZZThflKb2LU7w","children":[{"id":"13","parent":"12","text":"Criterios de Duke:","guid":"vmpCsBJhDlaxhy9y8ArPrQ","children":[{"id":"14","parent":"13","text":"Hemocultivos (+).","guid":"lNgcPHeAAcTcseroXfpliQ","children":[]},{"id":"15","parent":"13","text":"Evidencia de afectación endocárdica (eco).","guid":"pj9noFNdXvkvjGQ-kF8tfg","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"16","parent":"1","text":"Tratamiento","guid":"vqIHpfcfYHBG6dv_Rf0Rvw","children":[{"id":"17","parent":"16","text":"Antibióticos IV empíricos → ajustados según hemocultivo (+) → 4-6 semanas.","guid":"vmLY9CP0Q1h6I8PBV5Ku_Q","children":[]}]},{"id":"18","parent":"1","text":"Categorías:","guid":"Wu2_8E5EF2KRPX2y5uYJyQ","children":[{"id":"19","parent":"18","text":"Válvula nativa.","guid":"Ci-enJATkMLv0oGmuV4ymQ","children":[]},{"id":"20","parent":"18","text":"Prótesis valvular.","guid":"-Hmm2Xyb7_CLYJwnxjCifw","children":[]}]},{"id":"21","parent":"1","text":"Cx: Indicada en casos complejos (perforación valvular).","guid":"_aWfbKCwOGIDYCOHG2L4mg","children":[]},{"id":"22","parent":"1","text":"Profilaxis","guid":"2R5Y0Y6Na_MF3VMlncMGnw","children":[{"id":"23","parent":"22","text":"Pacientes con cardiopatías congénitas + procedimientos dentales específicos.","guid":"TxDirEpzjFaUovPzkkH97A","children":[]}]},{"id":"24","parent":"1","text":"Pronóstico","guid":"Te_08gObus3RYrzjoHuHiQ","children":[{"id":"25","parent":"24","text":"Mortal si no se trata.","guid":"mS_70XtUEKl0nfpPZ1oTEg","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"26","parent":"0","text":"Etiología - Patógenos en\\NEndocarditis Infecciosa (EI)","guid":"","children":[{"id":"27","parent":"26","text":"Staphylococcus\\Naureus","guid":"rvO-_HqmJXFsyhQsaKhf7A","children":[{"id":"28","parent":"27","text":"∼ 35-40% de EI en válvula nativa (1).","guid":"QqoM1VJxHWMJlksFBpRMUg","children":[]},{"id":"29","parent":"27","text":"Principal causa de EI aguda.","guid":"9YRKa4IuI5D2qlP-jDRjCg","children":[]},{"id":"30","parent":"27","text":"Afecta válvulas sanas.","guid":"YvQtal7UNgIqFekH8VR1RA","children":[]},{"id":"31","parent":"27","text":"Común en usuarios de drogas IV, prótesis\\Nvalvulares, marcapasos/DAI (2,3).","guid":"2keTUj6nMgtj9BKfh-GBow","children":[]},{"id":"32","parent":"27","text":"Mortal en ≤ 6 semanas sin tratamiento.","guid":"ZVNgCZWgYAPw7TbekzfYNw","children":[]}]},{"id":"33","parent":"26","text":"Streptococos\\Nviridans","guid":"jZYNruGOeEeRGCKhX3_Egg","children":[{"id":"34","parent":"33","text":"∼ 20% de EI en válvula nativa (1).","guid":"gJQbhdW4XcjLLuTuYDawXQ","children":[]},{"id":"35","parent":"33","text":"Causa principal de EI subaguda en válvulas\\Npreviamente dañadas (mitral).","guid":"BFHPAU9hWE8FpDRE_4HVvg","children":[]},{"id":"36","parent":"33","text":"Relacionada a procedimientos dentales,\\Nincisiones/biopsias respiratorias.","guid":"b0UKaZeMht044rIVMLe1KQ","children":[]},{"id":"37","parent":"33","text":"Produce dextranos → facilita unión a\\Nagregados fibrina-plaquetas en válvulas.","guid":"guIdm9F3Qm6S5ol-fm0KAA","children":[]}]},{"id":"38","parent":"26","text":"Staphylococcus\\Nepidermidis","guid":"P_Cer4CAmOPQMk-ZxZ0bYw","children":[{"id":"39","parent":"38","text":"< 15% de EI en válvula nativa (1).","guid":"1ObmPMF0OGT5EBhhlAEwZw","children":[]},{"id":"40","parent":"38","text":"Bacteriemia por catéteres venosos periféricos.","guid":"npjgpXS9Lr0zG0-jgKAz0A","children":[]},{"id":"41","parent":"38","text":"Causa común de EI subaguda en pacientes\\Ncon prótesis valvulares, marcapasos, DAI (4).","guid":"hv3DrTaQTmOckQSLvjrw7g","children":[]}]},{"id":"42","parent":"26","text":"Enterococos\\N(E. faecalis)","guid":"H35r26K9NaCOos9bdj_CSA","children":[{"id":"43","parent":"42","text":"∼ 10% de EI en válvula nativa (1).","guid":"WGIbDI_2h1Gq6iOHvGd8aQ","children":[]},{"id":"44","parent":"42","text":"Multirresistencia a fármacos.","guid":"_KaquyCJDCK2ig82gW-d9A","children":[]},{"id":"45","parent":"42","text":"Causa EI tras ITU nosocomial.","guid":"S4kdn3SRsSAQZCFHJwVoRg","children":[]},{"id":"46","parent":"42","text":"Relacionado a procedimientos GI o GU.","guid":"LcNt3rc9yaro487dqC6vRw","children":[]}]},{"id":"47","parent":"26","text":"Streptococcus\\Ngallolyticus (Sgg)","guid":"uxg1MOyRowSex8ORlpzFSw","children":[{"id":"48","parent":"47","text":"< 15% de EI en válvula nativa (1).","guid":"ccL_pfuERH9ZaOgUk64eEQ","children":[]},{"id":"49","parent":"47","text":"Asociado a cáncer colorrectal (6).","guid":"t2RRYG4E7BbhFFxqc4fXCg","children":[]},{"id":"50","parent":"47","text":"Detección de Sgg → requiere colonoscopía.","guid":"nE6fVV4BxRnPhD7-yFL9Fg","children":[]}]},{"id":"51","parent":"26","text":"Grupo HACEK\\N(Gram -)","guid":"tlqJ8C5ZR3GKkCbX9pNzHA","children":[{"id":"52","parent":"51","text":"< 5% de EI en válvula nativa (1,6).","guid":"9ZOWYFPrq5h6P52wQBwy_A","children":[]},{"id":"53","parent":"51","text":"Flora orofaríngea.","guid":"OAq6be_l3cx9my6qBudNqg","children":[]},{"id":"54","parent":"51","text":"Riesgo en mala higiene dental/infección periodontal.","guid":"mOzCENbIqd4awwZLuBE-3A","children":[]}]},{"id":"55","parent":"26","text":"Endocarditis fúngica\\N(Candida, Aspergillus)","guid":"OJaEHtknyuzJ-W6k9Pz0Gw","children":[{"id":"56","parent":"55","text":"< 5% de EI en válvula nativa (1).","guid":"SLYpOytVR6v-y3LO-aaPsQ","children":[]},{"id":"57","parent":"55","text":"Grupos de riesgo:","guid":"1vkhw8ExKGqorZZehY8LEA","children":[{"id":"58","parent":"57","text":"Pacientes inmunosuprimidos (HIV, trasplantes).","guid":"v-WqP5Zk8bJz78Q52ZC6bA","children":[]},{"id":"59","parent":"57","text":"Usuarios de drogas IV.","guid":"kXsvbkodVPgm1dDIWEk0bw","children":[]},{"id":"60","parent":"57","text":"Postcirugía cardíaca.","guid":"cI4goxLjTVHoLt7GtNVBmQ","children":[]},{"id":"61","parent":"57","text":"Catéteres IV a largo plazo (9).","guid":"NMrnwz7fix_qjARUIs2nAQ","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"62","parent":"26","text":"Coxiella burnetii/Bartonella spp.","guid":"7srZwuLydnYuBrLrzebyxw","children":[{"id":"63","parent":"62","text":"< 5% de EI en válvula nativa (1).","guid":"ME7M59Yy15SiWiUvgiFvmg","children":[]},{"id":"64","parent":"62","text":"Gram - responsables de endocarditis con hemocultivo negativo.","guid":"w-gKNc4I8wWoiFy-EzLxYg","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"65","parent":"0","text":"Factores de Riesgo para\\NEndocarditis Infecciosa (EI)","guid":"","children":[{"id":"66","parent":"65","text":"Demográficos","guid":"R5dZJHxqYi24QCwJjqq8sA","children":[{"id":"67","parent":"66","text":"Sexo masculino.","guid":"d1yzDP23aqRfbBr1Mgt0lg","children":[]},{"id":"68","parent":"66","text":"Edad > 60 años.","guid":"0JpuoBhGte7YVNQQM4g8ZA","children":[]}]},{"id":"69","parent":"65","text":"Condiciones\\Ncardíacas","guid":"nOVOfEEU8NvcHEXD-dnSOQ","children":[{"id":"70","parent":"69","text":"Enfermedades valvulares adquiridas (enf. reumática, estenosis aórtica, enfermedad valvular degenerativa).","guid":"2NuDMELFP9BZ6AuFW9xvaw","children":[]},{"id":"71","parent":"69","text":"Prótesis valvulares.","guid":"E4MlsXfLR2F8k1d3StwoRg","children":[]},{"id":"72","parent":"69","text":"Defectos cardíacos congénitos (e.g., CIV, válvula aórtica bicúspide).","guid":"Wdz0Lub5kT43gf83EBx4kw","children":[]},{"id":"73","parent":"69","text":"EI previa.","guid":"BOsz2miF8msT4Nw6kqCayA","children":[]},{"id":"74","parent":"69","text":"Dispositivo electrónico implantable cardíaco (CIED) (4).","guid":"MZwqCJsKJJv5ZKjuTGrkYg","children":[]}]},{"id":"75","parent":"65","text":"Factores no\\Ncardíacos","guid":"lpiu04DoY-8i662Wdco5aw","children":[{"id":"76","parent":"75","text":"Mala salud dental.","guid":"Jkb0mWTYFzapm_DzQuz2WQ","children":[]},{"id":"77","parent":"75","text":"Procedimientos dentales.","guid":"scJedQQZ2q4ziwjoSW5VWg","children":[]},{"id":"78","parent":"75","text":"Inyecciones venosas no estériles (uso IV de drogas).","guid":"ISJJeixoaenE_3Ko4ob9jA","children":[]},{"id":"79","parent":"75","text":"Dispositivos intravasculares.","guid":"LrpMij-t5zTI_n0of6HYaA","children":[]},{"id":"80","parent":"75","text":"Cirugía.","guid":"chq0h8gu3m4-4RNVNNQzfQ","children":[]},{"id":"81","parent":"75","text":"Hemodiálisis crónica.","guid":"D4LnqcbI4PRpxGkIeUN9Og","children":[]},{"id":"82","parent":"75","text":"Inmunocompromiso (infección VIH, DM).","guid":"lUDpfw8FNYsjgVstKYO-Sw","children":[]},{"id":"83","parent":"75","text":"Infecciones bacterianas (e.g., ITU, espondilodiscitis, infecciones periodontales).","guid":"7xAEo8F6t7SMWKknKFAOQA","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"84","parent":"0","text":"Fisiopatología de\\NEndocarditis Infecciosa\\N(EI)","guid":"","children":[{"id":"85","parent":"84","text":"Patogénesis (1, 11)","guid":"b9iz6pYNpEnh5C1zqGYmlg","children":[{"id":"86","parent":"85","text":"Daño endotelial valvular → exposición de capa subendotelial → adhesión de plaquetas y fibrina → vegetación estéril (microtrombo).","guid":"_6n_53NW9r4NsQytz77VxA","children":[]},{"id":"87","parent":"85","text":"Infección localizada o contaminación → bacteriemia → colonización bacteriana de vegetación → formación de coágulos de fibrina que encapsulan la vegetación\\N→ destrucción valvular con pérdida de función (insuficiencia valvular).","guid":"_m1addAFIrJKiRQoOoHtww","children":[]}]},{"id":"88","parent":"84","text":"Afectación valvular (10)","guid":"Y6nGCd9YN_OdSW-nGQO8-g","children":[{"id":"89","parent":"88","text":"Frecuencia de afectación: válvula mitral > válvula aórtica > válvula tricúspide > válvula pulmonar.","guid":"bPrC4jFpvf2ZbqbxisZT4w","children":[]},{"id":"90","parent":"88","text":"Válvula tricúspide: más afectada en usuarios de drogas IV (asociada a Pseudomonas, S. aureus, Candida).","guid":"9XoBIuI3YRt0Gr-00iW6iw","children":[]}]},{"id":"91","parent":"84","text":"Consecuencias\\Nclínicas (1, 11)","guid":"w-xGHsvCHkvZImsTBKXXpg","children":[{"id":"92","parent":"91","text":"Vegetación bacteriana → tromboembolia bacteriana → oclusión vascular → infartos.","guid":"ozEnR7as-6RntAgRMbOjFQ","children":[]},{"id":"93","parent":"91","text":"Los émbolos pueden causar infecciones metastásicas en otros órganos.","guid":"gIRxVdyrvXaJSYJ-cu-37g","children":[]},{"id":"94","parent":"91","text":"Formación de complejos inmunes y anticuerpos contra antígenos tisulares → glomerulonefritis, nódulos de Osler.","guid":"Dgv2Bztb6QqbUsUQ72mpkw","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"95","parent":"0","text":"Características Clínicas de\\NEndocarditis Infecciosa (EI)","guid":"","children":[{"id":"96","parent":"95","text":"Síntomas constitucionales\\N(1, 12)","guid":"jMCQ2s-_msx__KfBeAHUog","children":[{"id":"97","parent":"96","text":"Fiebre y escalofríos.","guid":"oYb_-CVvXMvMN0Qo74q4dg","children":[]},{"id":"98","parent":"96","text":"Taquicardia.","guid":"_ieSu5C0Bau-8yqjSLXZFQ","children":[]},{"id":"99","parent":"96","text":"Malestar general, debilidad, pérdida de peso, sudores nocturnos.","guid":"ApIcET8EeRF3TWCSkJsxsQ","children":[]},{"id":"100","parent":"96","text":"Disnea, tos, dolor torácico pleurítico.","guid":"FMkoLRHziO8Z_Lsk_upogA","children":[]},{"id":"101","parent":"96","text":"Artralgias, mialgias.","guid":"qOfwFxZ4JsUhb_29rj1SKg","children":[]}]},{"id":"102","parent":"95","text":"Manifestaciones\\Ncardíacas (1, 12)","guid":"JKOxW0Gj2_XVol8o2sUrtg","children":[{"id":"103","parent":"102","text":"Soplo cardíaco (nuevo o\\Ncambio en soplo preexistente).","guid":"a4rwQgW9GqzFpa3sqADNsg","children":[{"id":"104","parent":"103","text":"Insuficiencia tricuspídea: soplo holosistólico, más fuerte en borde esternal izquierdo; común en usuarios\\Nde drogas IV, inmunocomprometidos, cardiopatía congénita o catéteres venosos centrales (2).","guid":"HRk4AyKbkDFC0BzwhTj0OQ","children":[]},{"id":"105","parent":"103","text":"Insuficiencia aórtica: soplo diastólico precoz, más fuerte en\\Nespacios intercostales 3º y 4º izquierdos, borde esternal (4).","guid":"LOf626_GihqVXF3xBgCcMg","children":[]},{"id":"106","parent":"103","text":"Insuficiencia mitral: soplo holosistólico, más fuerte en ápex, irradiado a axila izquierda.","guid":"4cbOQ-f3gPOZtHZAIVOvUA","children":[]}]},{"id":"107","parent":"102","text":"Insuficiencia cardíaca: disnea, edema de EEII por insuficiencia valvular.","guid":"Tx_I-XqQ9qp-yLc9OGLAxA","children":[]},{"id":"108","parent":"102","text":"Arritmias: sospecha de absceso perivalvular si hay nuevo trastorno de conducción (bloqueo cardíaco) (14).","guid":"JepRCAeG_X7ia1ngi9OlGw","children":[]}]},{"id":"109","parent":"95","text":"Manifestaciones\\Nextracardíacas (1, 12, 15)","guid":"gqVkEeQIU19z61enN5Fcxg","children":[{"id":"110","parent":"109","text":"Fenómenos embólicos e inmunológicos periféricos\\N(5-10% pacientes).","guid":"zcjofWAJAGhnnfU1T9_hfw","children":[]},{"id":"111","parent":"109","text":"Petequias, hemorragias en astilla (subungueales).","guid":"YeaLymJOn1W9M0BUgyVTLw","children":[]},{"id":"112","parent":"109","text":"Lesiones de Janeway: máculas eritematosas, no dolorosas, en palmas y plantas\\N(microabscesos por émbolos sépticos).","guid":"dnzoo67LJc3WAFgc7IgUDw","children":[]},{"id":"113","parent":"109","text":"Nódulos de Osler: nódulos dolorosos en pulpejos de dedos y pies\\N(depósitos de complejos inmunes).","guid":"2Q0ZtCm37AnOvdfKfS9gPQ","children":[]},{"id":"114","parent":"109","text":"Manchas de Roth: hemorragias retinianas redondas con centro pálido.","guid":"t39AfdzqLkAmYHobqS6ldw","children":[]}]},{"id":"115","parent":"95","text":"Embolias a órganos\\Nintraabdominales:","guid":"jGVsE3Szm15AiHj73y47Qw","children":[{"id":"116","parent":"115","text":"Lesión renal aguda: hematuria/anuria\\N(oclusión de arteria renal o glomerulonefritis).","guid":"kwp-Hx-gqYy3m4LWwhiPRQ","children":[]},{"id":"117","parent":"115","text":"Esplenomegalia y dolor CSD: oclusión de arteria esplénica o\\Nabsceso esplénico; riesgo de ruptura esplénica (16).","guid":"RcVY5VXtTTiF0m0pAtoKTg","children":[]}]},{"id":"118","parent":"95","text":"Manifestaciones neurológicas: convulsiones, paresias\\N(ACV embólico séptico, meningitis, encefalitis, absceso).","guid":"xERJBsyGT5W32h4-gNgdxw","children":[]},{"id":"119","parent":"95","text":"Manifestaciones pulmonares\\N(involucramiento tricuspídeo):","guid":"kARCMulLYcLJwVUJjgJgIA","children":[{"id":"120","parent":"119","text":"Signos de embolia pulmonar (disnea).","guid":"ANUFHx_2T0mL3vFAxZx-hQ","children":[]},{"id":"121","parent":"119","text":"Infección pulmonar: neumonía multifocal,\\Nabsceso pulmonar, empiema (19).","guid":"Jxt-ij6BnzghjsvXHJT5JA","children":[]}]},{"id":"122","parent":"95","text":"Otras: Artritis.","guid":"kQt8QRjnwUxP3uk0A-q3Fw","children":[]},{"id":"123","parent":"95","text":"Recuerda: EI como causa de fiebre de origen desconocido (FOD),\\Nespecialmente con nuevo soplo cardíaco.","guid":"ZDtenxxOW13QBtzSjpwk3A","children":[]}]},{"id":"124","parent":"0","text":"Clasificación de la\\NEndocarditis Infecciosa (EI)","guid":"","children":[{"id":"125","parent":"124","text":"Por tipo de válvula y\\Ncurso clínico (15)","guid":"Q8mZp1W8Aqn2pnrsSTs6Zw","children":[{"id":"126","parent":"125","text":"Endocarditis en\\Nválvula nativa","guid":"Sq76OJcQ4099-w1OBCOpJg","children":[]},{"id":"127","parent":"125","text":"Endocarditis en\\Nválvula protésica","guid":"Evw0kkjEvFyq2g8HsIGltA","children":[]}]},{"id":"128","parent":"124","text":"De inicio temprano: ≤ 1 año post-cirugía.","guid":"nGsjPL8EQ6dQZuvQJKvItw","children":[{"id":"129","parent":"128","text":"De inicio tardío: > 1 año post-cirugía.","guid":"sExuYyLvwdlZzKfX7D88TQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"130","parent":"124","text":"Por agudeza\\Nde la infección","guid":"OaTdQASieg7wUYzCgS27zQ","children":[{"id":"131","parent":"130","text":"Endocarditis\\Nbacteriana aguda","guid":"8IP-VhhXunIuovoBvQr2Tw","children":[{"id":"132","parent":"131","text":"Inicio agudo.","guid":"wesCRtKmLBMT2oISlKmqkg","children":[]},{"id":"133","parent":"131","text":"Progresión rápida, fulminante (días a semanas).","guid":"BVTqSIDsqKRf1bWhEUYjmQ","children":[]},{"id":"134","parent":"131","text":"Síntomas constitucionales severos (fiebre alta).","guid":"ZLzBZk5eQbjY7_2NnPUbSA","children":[]}]},{"id":"135","parent":"130","text":"Endocarditis\\Nbacteriana subaguda","guid":"73bH7hzjWufxErZ59k9eJg","children":[{"id":"136","parent":"135","text":"Inicio insidioso.","guid":"uwK7xoJVyut5loOwMTmbWg","children":[]},{"id":"137","parent":"135","text":"Progresión lenta (semanas a meses).","guid":"pllhCSCS0AXxDItc3mAAJw","children":[]},{"id":"138","parent":"135","text":"Síntomas constitucionales menos severos\\N(fiebre baja, malestar, disnea, pérdida de peso).","guid":"h1h-peeNSL-OJHo-at5DZQ","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"139","parent":"124","text":"Patógenos\\Nprincipales","guid":"ydpZpNlOXScbPdAjG-43IA","children":[{"id":"140","parent":"139","text":"Aguda:","guid":"G9hoVxNBpAWotCQCsARJIA","children":[{"id":"141","parent":"140","text":"S. aureus (asociado a grandes vegetaciones, destrucción valvular).","guid":"SbaVPGadboLXz8KZajGq2Q","children":[]},{"id":"142","parent":"140","text":"Otros: Streptococcus β-hemolítico grupo A, S. pneumoniae, N. gonorrhoeae.","guid":"T9QhvZ7PdJZ3shNqXjWzBw","children":[]}]},{"id":"143","parent":"139","text":"Subaguda:","guid":"D1L3f8oDCxSa6WOThOeUEA","children":[{"id":"144","parent":"143","text":"Streptococcus viridans, S. aureus, Enterococos, grupo HACEK.","guid":"PeJ0IAlAVPeR114WQr0Lzw","children":[]}]},{"id":"145","parent":"139","text":"Válvula protésica temprana: Staphylococcus coagulasa-negativa, S. aureus, bacilos gram-negativos.","guid":"FB4nvV3IUqtEB49uAuQjOw","children":[]},{"id":"146","parent":"139","text":"Válvula protésica tardía: Staphylococcus coagulasa-negativa, S. aureus, Streptococcus viridans.","guid":"QKd8v5Z7T_y4DL8X5t0D5g","children":[]}]},{"id":"147","parent":"124","text":"Válvulas afectadas","guid":"HxQ6Uje5WJ3TWdd6eD11gw","children":[{"id":"148","parent":"147","text":"Válvula nativa: sana o con daño previo/defectos congénitos.","guid":"GSyeMnqVluXQK5QHHXM1nQ","children":[]},{"id":"149","parent":"147","text":"Válvula protésica: válvulas mecánicas o bioprotésicas.","guid":"3dBlJgIqZnYzzGkz9L53jA","children":[]}]},{"id":"150","parent":"124","text":"Por localización","guid":"TG-uZAuxuS2i7Nvsj4kddw","children":[{"id":"151","parent":"150","text":"EI derecha (20)","guid":"9wtNfD8arbSXJGUBP3AJHA","children":[{"id":"152","parent":"151","text":"Características clí