,"parent":"179","text":"Condición predisponente (e. g., anomalía cardíaca, uso de drogas IV) (23).","guid":"rFbjbCX1AxniBMGzUum8EQ","children":[]},{"id":"181","parent":"179","text":"Fiebre > 38°C.","guid":"MvGaPgTaLYxrvd-hcDU-OQ","children":[]},{"id":"182","parent":"179","text":"Anomalías vasculares.","guid":"LY77DIGp5yIbZbaECRUdDw","children":[]},{"id":"183","parent":"179","text":"Fenómenos inmunológicos.","guid":"Ncy9DUlERH-t_aNxA4XCyQ","children":[]},{"id":"184","parent":"179","text":"Microbiología: hemocultivos positivos sin cumplir criterios mayores o\\Nevidencia serológica de infección con organismos comunes.","guid":"8SVxSjO57D4qz77PQDeQmg","children":[]}]},{"id":"185","parent":"168","text":"Criterios\\Npatológicos","guid":"ahkIhzjnvbQpSn3_cdRq4Q","children":[{"id":"186","parent":"185","text":"Microorganismos demostrados por cultivo tisular o histología.","guid":"UzB1hvjMtj8XqohJnbAyjg","children":[]},{"id":"187","parent":"185","text":"Características histológicas de EI activa.","guid":"-Fujfuw5XKWO0TB22Hh_yQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"188","parent":"168","text":"Categorías\\Ndiagnósticas","guid":"KLAiIH0YzRry8mDQ1-omcw","children":[{"id":"189","parent":"188","text":"EI definitiva si:","guid":"WVa1Dqh8gWdY6ojpSSFy3g","children":[{"id":"190","parent":"189","text":"≥ 2 criterios mayores.","guid":"wnyutnMiai72QGucwVUdUw","children":[]},{"id":"191","parent":"189","text":"≥ 1 criterio mayor + ≥ 3 criterios menores.","guid":"XiDs0NpjnRhQegEzh1nteA","children":[]},{"id":"192","parent":"189","text":"≥ 5 criterios menores.","guid":"K4m1b93gFg2O0-Y7fD3pGg","children":[]},{"id":"193","parent":"189","text":"≥ 1 criterio patológico.","guid":"8TmIT0_RwaXhsqJgokiX4Q","children":[]}]},{"id":"194","parent":"188","text":"EI posible si:","guid":"3rvRgLAlwrpELAeNy_CshA","children":[{"id":"195","parent":"194","text":"≥ 1 criterio mayor + ≥ 1\\Ncriterio menor.","guid":"sUeQKgn7JHbXiTORiD_R1A","children":[]},{"id":"196","parent":"194","text":"≥ 3 criterios menores.","guid":"UAFz7gpemdXqSpMyrdX4_Q","children":[]}]}]}]},{"id":"197","parent":"161","text":"Estudios de\\Nlaboratorio (15)","guid":"ZgrMuPPYES48o2Ay5LFaHA","children":[{"id":"198","parent":"197","text":"Hemograma completo (CBC): leucocitosis con desviación izquierda.","guid":"6_vQ8V-my-Htm0R2gG1Pgg","children":[]},{"id":"199","parent":"197","text":"Marcadores inflamatorios: ⬆️ CRP, ⬆️ VSG (21).","guid":"75CVH4hjdos0tVbp9t2cLQ","children":[]},{"id":"200","parent":"197","text":"Análisis de orina: hematuria, sedimento nefrítico (13, 24).","guid":"JxbYqPdSypME3TohWuLalg","children":[]},{"id":"201","parent":"197","text":"Hemocultivos (25)","guid":"1PLzBoqa0Q4hf8rs4qOEfg","children":[{"id":"202","parent":"201","text":"Protocolo de muestreo:","guid":"96bRCbhylAgktDgj-SqzYQ","children":[{"id":"203","parent":"202","text":"Pre-tratamiento: 3 sets de diferentes sitios de venopunción.","guid":"Fz4Ds1Mun6wenraZwiMtRw","children":[]},{"id":"204","parent":"202","text":"Monitoreo: 2 sets cada 24-48 h hasta aclaramiento.","guid":"AqX0fLvNBg8V6SRTfbdTPA","children":[]}]},{"id":"205","parent":"201","text":"Interpretación:","guid":"Sj4YrwdtSIJ7pTDMULjJBg","children":[{"id":"206","parent":"205","text":"Hemocultivos (+): evaluar según los criterios de Duke modificados.","guid":"cBm9JZT7IzXMXPjMJgeZ_Q","children":[]},{"id":"207","parent":"205","text":"Hemocultivos (-) no excluyen EI;\\Nposible por:","guid":"88nXjX6kcrRoXxR_3dsVgA","children":[{"id":"208","parent":"207","text":"Terapia ATB previa.","guid":"eZ1Z0NVPPSjnncs56osZOQ","children":[]},{"id":"209","parent":"207","text":"Bacterias exigentes (Coxiella burnetii, Bartonella spp.) (6, 26, 25).","guid":"6YHf_rwN0H_cf3SRT2PGng","children":[]}]}]}]}]},{"id":"210","parent":"161","text":"Ecocardiografía\\N(15)","guid":"VfT2U9YDZEVxBHZDE7syxg","children":[{"id":"211","parent":"210","text":"Ecocardiografía transtorácica (TTE):\\Nprueba inicial en sospecha de EI.","guid":"X6shvAyLDhLp8x7sQRcE3Q","children":[]},{"id":"212","parent":"210","text":"Ecocardiografía transesofágica (TEE):\\Nmás invasiva, indicada si:","guid":"o0U03xNj79vzyIAmjHXCXw","children":[{"id":"213","parent":"212","text":"Características de alto riesgo.","guid":"HsgsImOgrH4xgj4UtQ_AKQ","children":[]},{"id":"214","parent":"212","text":"Hallazgos del TTE inconclusos o sugerentes de EI.","guid":"TiUFbOODixTjZxzzPXbKYA","children":[]},{"id":"215","parent":"212","text":"Preocupación por complicaciones intracardíacas (e.g., absceso).","guid":"Vo-R_golBp4LN2P2Vv_ttQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"216","parent":"210","text":"Hallazgos ecocardiográficos\\N(Duke):","guid":"KULVaBPbU-tAY8UuqBPZjg","children":[{"id":"217","parent":"216","text":"Vegetaciones valvulares: masas móviles hiperecoicas en válvula, endocardio mural o material protésico (6, 27, 28).","guid":"9CWny-bWcClZyXrSOx8qLw","children":[]},{"id":"218","parent":"216","text":"Absceso (e.g., absceso perivalvular).","guid":"mqkw8f9Az-ngztFR89nAtg","children":[]},{"id":"219","parent":"216","text":"Nueva regurgitación valvular (prolapso, perforación, destrucción).","guid":"Vy4Lq2hPGdx12Ea5D8dA8w","children":[]},{"id":"220","parent":"216","text":"Dehiscencia de válvula protésica.","guid":"F4szX5S6Vsb7zooRxJ5r6Q","children":[]}]},{"id":"221","parent":"210","text":"Sensibilidad:","guid":"CsbWShx7RwZ6y5mUOF7cDA","children":[{"id":"222","parent":"221","text":"TEE: ∼90%","guid":"1GPeTlEDNfl5imjay69z0w","children":[{"id":"223","parent":"222","text":"TEE más fiable para descartar EI en pacientes con probabilidad moderada-alta.","guid":"ak31WM6SjpwF8ElbPLfCEQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"224","parent":"221","text":"TTE: ∼75%","guid":"u_KjxnRNiRlCysnhA_sEPQ","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"225","parent":"161","text":"Patología\\N(31)","guid":"IxKpJseP88h7tggTZKpw-g","children":[{"id":"226","parent":"225","text":"Enfermedad aguda:","guid":"X_dWx6ZaIzjNqbvY4TTSTw","children":[{"id":"227","parent":"226","text":"Insuficiencia valvular, infartos embólicos sépticos, ruptura de cuerdas tendinosas.","guid":"XLu3aH18AjYBP1LZjkJHlQ","children":[]},{"id":"228","parent":"226","text":"Erosión → depósitos de fibrina, ulceración, perforación.","guid":"eiFs2XlfgFZhoziUrPv2Cg","children":[]}]},{"id":"229","parent":"225","text":"Enfermedad crónica:","guid":"rsPvF8vCZTdN4Eg8HXM2XQ","children":[{"id":"230","parent":"229","text":"Insuficiencia/estenosis valvular.","guid":"S6NixzN8HBscaJ6AOF53RA","children":[]},{"id":"231","parent":"229","text":"Erosión → reorganización fibrina, tejido de granulación → fibrosis/cicatrización valvular.","guid":"vUrwIjdSh6-5PRxZIZL9YQ","children":[]},{"id":"232","parent":"229","text":"Calcificación → cuerdas tendinosas gruesas/acortadas.","guid":"67_oZQ_-FiCvufJfnx78Ug","children":[]}]}]}]},{"id":"233","parent":"0","text":"Diagnósticos diferenciales\\N(32, 33, 34)","guid":"1MvDEBBWSQzeUg30RF4akw","children":[{"id":"234","parent":"233","text":"Endocarditis no infecciosa\\N(trombótica no bacteriana):","guid":"Z0xlLx5H4NAI4oSPk7Rftg","children":[{"id":"235","parent":"234","text":"Descripción: trombos estériles en válvulas cardíacas (usualmente mitral/aórtica).","guid":"r3-lsQsN5N2DhO11mFy0tQ","children":[]},{"id":"236","parent":"234","text":"Endocarditis de Libman-Sacks: vegetaciones verrugosas en LES o síndrome antifosfolípidos.","guid":"7cJnYcYeviRm8mhoBk8iEg","children":[]},{"id":"237","parent":"234","text":"Etiología: malignidad, estados hipercoagulables, trauma valvular, fiebre reumática, enfermedades autoinmunes\\N(e.g., LES, AR), infecciones crónicas (e.g. , TB, neumonía, osteomielitis).","guid":"8W8jwtNl5pbXhQwmSHYWLQ","children":[]},{"id":"238","parent":"234","text":"Características clínicas: vegetaciones se desprenden fácilmente → embolización común\\N(hemorragias subungueales, cutáneas, retinianas); pacientes asintomáticos hasta embolización.","guid":"Nfkrwp4KB7hSFg_xTEAO5w","children":[]},{"id":"239","parent":"234","text":"Diagnóstico:","guid":"vwCSc1cG6n37nKp0N_uejw","children":[{"id":"240","parent":"239","text":"Hemocultivos (-).","guid":"HHUcLq69wXFt04icPYAfGQ","children":[]},{"id":"241","parent":"239","text":"Ecocardiografía: vegetaciones.","guid":"jt3WcP8FSLEpktHePfpWqQ","children":[]},{"id":"242","parent":"239","text":"Biopsia: diagnóstico definitivo (vegetaciones estériles compuestas de complejos inmunes, células mononucleares, trombos intercalados con fibrina).","guid":"1Ti9U69FbCLsMxCWDimWiQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"243","parent":"234","text":"Tratamiento: anticoagulación con heparina + tratar condición subyacente.","guid":"Cpe_ePL9ZdGeDVpKE0qLMg","children":[]}]},{"id":"244","parent":"233","text":"Otros diferenciales:","guid":"2lyR3Cm9Hp5mQGFCaZuN1w","children":[{"id":"245","parent":"244","text":"Infección de catéter intravascular.","guid":"HfnTRPgUlNeo8BrP7dZVbQ","children":[]},{"id":"246","parent":"244","text":"Infección de prótesis (válvulas, articulaciones, dispositivos electrónicos cardíacos).","guid":"RctvvS4SgZesgNDC3PkZDw","children":[]},{"id":"247","parent":"244","text":"Trombosis de válvula protésica.","guid":"Zohz55C_2L6Q1A1s0N2yLw","children":[]},{"id":"248","parent":"244","text":"Osteomielitis hematógena.","guid":"rEMfHEy93eLTe-gxk_5yCA","children":[]},{"id":"249","parent":"244","text":"Tromboflebitis séptica.","guid":"UPkBpLxzTJUMLDGKK3Pnsw","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"250","parent":"0","text":"Manejo","guid":"z2vkKO7oNoDBIQEbAelKxQ","children":[{"id":"251","parent":"250","text":"Manejo inicial\\N(6, 15, 35, 36)","guid":"Rwctzaj9N51vdqTJ3XV-bA","children":[{"id":"252","parent":"251","text":"Pacientes inestables: Abordar con el enfoque ABCDE, iniciar manejo de sepsis si es necesario.","guid":"BfE4uUdkiNi_UAXsimTZ6A","children":[]},{"id":"253","parent":"251","text":"Consultar infectología tempranamente para planificar tratamiento y considerar terapia empírica.","guid":"w-jl6CN4pbiwK-AHAlAZdQ","children":[]},{"id":"254","parent":"251","text":"Identificar pacientes que requieren consulta quirúrgica.","guid":"nHmmuRM0MzcXwpKvhCp6rQ","children":[]},{"id":"255","parent":"251","text":"Terapia\\Nantibiótica:","guid":"nTi5Sw3Xm-Ta9Fl--FQrOA","children":[{"id":"256","parent":"255","text":"Iniciar ATB empírica después de tomar hemocultivos.","guid":"7EdGKYFvf2Kts38mB47Mgw","children":[]},{"id":"257","parent":"255","text":"Cambiar a ATB dirigida una vez disponibles los resultados de los hemocultivos.","guid":"iY50fdSODkj2HIY5aqtmBg","children":[]}]},{"id":"258","parent":"251","text":"Cuidados de soporte: Tratar complicaciones urgentes (e.g., IC aguda, bloqueo cardíaco) y la causa subyacente (e. g., retiro de catéteres infectados).","guid":"JxZ91WcOhO8hKGKGco5EKg","children":[]}]},{"id":"259","parent":"250","text":"Terapia antibiótica\\N(6, 36)","guid":"xuajVNTftA4oCOinwldkQQ","children":[{"id":"260","parent":"259","text":"Elección de ATB empírico: Consultar a infectología, considerar factores del paciente y enfermedad,\\Nasí como flora y patrones de resistencia locales/individuales.","guid":"McQDusgpw4LqhzBUxZWpOg","children":[]},{"id":"261","parent":"259","text":"Endocarditis en válvula nativa: vancomicina + beta-lactámico (e.g., ceftriaxona, cefepime).","guid":"7nz4iVlqebPql3M4Y2uMfw","children":[]},{"id":"262","parent":"259","text":"Endocarditis en válvula protésica: añadir gentamicina + rifampicina a\\Nvancomicina + beta-lactámico (si ≤ 1 año post-implante).","guid":"wLp8NaV4wmQWmprvcM6Odw","children":[]},{"id":"263","parent":"259","text":"Regímenes ATB\\Ndirigidos comunes:","guid":"VnHpdh2etJdsiocA8AbVuw","children":[{"id":"264","parent":"263","text":"Estafilococos:","guid":"eufnHhPYqdLGxfBm5jRLQA","children":[{"id":"265","parent":"264","text":"MSSA: beta-lactámico antistafilocócico (e.g., nafcilina, oxacilina).","guid":"si00Du8G37Ev80S05zpQGg","children":[]},{"id":"266","parent":"264","text":"MRSA: vancomicina.","guid":"1aCthO16S2ytrvFfeAVKvA","children":[]},{"id":"267","parent":"264","text":"Endocarditis en válvula protésica (≤ 1 año): añadir gentamicina\\N+ rifampicina al régimen descrito para válvula nativa.","guid":"JRFHwkvdt5J3s7wrpOIoJg","children":[]}]},{"id":"268","parent":"263","text":"Streptococos viridans: beta-lactámico (e. g., penicilina G, ampicilina).","guid":"GsNs_nbfCjIHmRKcYirEtw","children":[]},{"id":"269","parent":"263","text":"Enterococos: terapia combinada (e.g., ampicilina + gentamicina).","guid":"OFHT6NjFb0pgTPD723rHWg","children":[]},{"id":"270","parent":"263","text":"HACEK: ceftriaxona (1ª línea).","guid":"ho1JiAnAx3Qv2tIAlDNrAQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"271","parent":"259","text":"Duración del tratamiento: variable (2–6 semanas o más) dependiendo\\Nde factores como el régimen, válvula afectada, entre otros.","guid":"0oaGYXV0DRQ98aNerZkQMg","children":[]}]},{"id":"272","parent":"250","text":"Cirugía\\N(15, 35, 37)","guid":"SNUlr64sUpyEj6k9_hYBYA","children":[{"id":"273","parent":"272","text":"Indicaciones para\\Nconsulta quirúrgica:","guid":"HqDvvZs7iIBXp_lwXUQesw","children":[{"id":"274","parent":"273","text":"Endocarditis en válvula protésica.","guid":"Kw2RxflnnMIFYbBprSBC1g","children":[]},{"id":"275","parent":"273","text":"Disfunción valvular → insuficiencia cardíaca.","guid":"rUrDv_iGAJzVB9AoFeTbzA","children":[]},{"id":"276","parent":"273","text":"Infección no controlada (e.g., vegetación en crecimiento, bacteriemia persistente).","guid":"X6whZEh7Nam8VS7GXsCoBQ","children":[]},{"id":"277","parent":"273","text":"Complicaciones perivalvulares (e.g., absceso, pseudoaneurisma, fístula, bloqueo cardíaco).","guid":"DXXcQHZf5eHC8mZoDxmmGA","children":[]},{"id":"278","parent":"273","text":"Endocarditis fúngica.","guid":"IsE3P2A1FJWtdgvoBvFyQA","children":[]},{"id":"279","parent":"273","text":"Alto riesgo embólico (e.g., vegetación móvil\\N> 10 mm, embolismos recurrentes).","guid":"JTD761-c3SAHRQvzL-wgug","children":[]}]},{"id":"280","parent":"272","text":"Opciones quirúrgicas: reemplazo o reparación valvular.","guid":"Es5GejTZcU2XdZq1DbE2sA","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"281","parent":"0","text":"Prevención (35,\\N43, 44, 45)","guid":"jmA5k7vcBRUlI0Nup6tg9w","children":[{"id":"282","parent":"281","text":"Factores de riesgo cardíaco que\\Nrequieren profilaxis para EI:","guid":"pqfETFoVm476y4zegWD9Pg","children":[{"id":"283","parent":"282","text":"Prótesis valvulares cardíacas o\\Nmateriales protésicos.","guid":"7k3jp3movcqUuTEaBk-ArQ","children":[]},{"id":"284","parent":"282","text":"Historia de EI.","guid":"mGexl3sAr_9-CovUMl3UYA","children":[]},{"id":"285","parent":"282","text":"Cardiopatías congénitas específicas (e.g., CHD cianótica no reparada,\\NCHD reparada < 6 meses o con cortocircuito residual postquirúrgico).","guid":"-AtRr60hlHqaxDnmuIp7UQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"286","parent":"281","text":"Procedimientos que\\Nrequieren profilaxis:","guid":"kccHFqqsgvBttZrEXPCFZw","children":[{"id":"287","parent":"286","text":"Procedimientos dentales (e.g. , extracción dental, limpieza dental rutinaria).","guid":"cqvYWLTUSNnEzdCh0UerDA","children":[]},{"id":"288","parent":"286","text":"Procedimientos invasivos en tejido infectado (e.g., drenaje de absceso).","guid":"n_FTAXvuOSV9JBxeUxpwcg","children":[]},{"id":"289","parent":"286","text":"Colocación de CIED.","guid":"NEXUQwn6o-08aY5b4kLeEQ","children":[]},{"id":"290","parent":"286","text":"Cirugía de implantes cardíacos o material intravascular (e.g., válvula, injerto).","guid":"rkS08MtLTjafjqmIoAy-7Q","children":[]}]},{"id":"291","parent":"281","text":"Regímenes comunes (30-60\\Nminutos antes del procedimiento):","guid":"bkwnq3WaNfMWwjK1_3epiQ","children":[{"id":"292","parent":"291","text":"Procedimientos\\Ndentales:","guid":"U0x0p2Oo8s4BNttYKOYZAw","children":[{"id":"293","parent":"292","text":"Sin alergia a penicilina: amoxicilina o ampicilina o cefazolina.","guid":"ySBm1VKKPPdTNAQGzhlQxA","children":[]},{"id":"294","parent":"292","text":"Con alergia a penicilina: macrólido (e.g., azitromicina) o doxiciclina.","guid":"wtmJk-O5PzbXWNJlegF_UA","children":[]}]},{"id":"295","parent":"291","text":"Colocación de CIED: cefazolina.","guid":"Pydnc37xDpFbefqIPn1nBg","children":[]}]},{"id":"296","parent":"281","text":"La profilaxis de EI no se recomienda de manera rutinaria en\\Nprocedimientos no dentales a menos que haya tejido infectado.","guid":"l2avLQ02YNgOLgOe720GeA","children":[]}]}]},"node_count":296,"relations":[],"cross_references":[],"specialty":"General","folder":"Entidades clínicas/General","filename":"EI-2024","id":"map_729","resolved_references":[]}